    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "公孙越",
        "吕翔",
        "四龙套",
        "报子",
        "袁绍"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、袁绍同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四世三公，保汉室，统领雄兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金盔凤翅锦罗袍，四世三公辅汉朝。谋臣战将归帐下，统领雄兵美名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾，袁绍。镇守河北一带等处。只因韩馥坐守冀州，此人性情柔弱，不称其职。\n吾久有攻取之意，但是无有机会，师出无名。\n左右，伺候了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有北平公孙越，前来求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。公孙越上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。未知将军驾到，有失远迎，当面恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙越",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。末将来得卤莽，明公恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。将军到此，必有所为。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙越",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今奉兄长之命，前来有书信呈上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待吾看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急三枪〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。吾修书不及，照书行事，便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙越",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公孙越下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公孙瓒要与我借兵，共取冀州，真道岂有此理。\n来，传吕翔进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕将军进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕翔上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领五百弓箭手，假扮作马腾兵马，在山后埋伏。等公孙越到来，将他射\n死，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕翔下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（袁绍、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
