    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "公孙越",
        "吕翔"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、吕翔同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，吕翔。奉了元帅将令，假扮马腾人马，截杀公孙越。\n众将官，山后埋伏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手、公孙越同上，会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙越",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人，敢挡我的去路？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃马腾帐下，大将庞德是也！奉主之命，特来杀你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙越",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满口胡言，看剑！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕翔败下，公孙越追下。吕翔上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，弓箭手伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公孙越追上，四上手同射箭，公孙越下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公孙越已死，回营交令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕翔、四上手同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "吕翔→公孙越",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "公孙越→吕翔",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
