    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "你弟被他把命送",
        "公孙瓒",
        "吕翔",
        "我命二弟把信送",
        "文丑",
        "老爷兴兵威风勇",
        "英雄岂在容貌上",
        "袁绍",
        "赵云",
        "颜良"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（颜良上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大将生来力刚强，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（文丑上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赫赫威名振四方。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吕翔上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阵前统带兵和将，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "单枪匹马把名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良、文丑、吕翔、赵云",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺——"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文丑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕翔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕翔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云。"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "文丑、吕翔、赵云",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "颜良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日元帅发兵，你我两厢伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四龙套、四上手同上，袁绍上。〖点绛唇〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾，袁绍。只因公孙瓒兴兵前来，要与他兄弟报仇，不免起兵前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云为何阻令？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那公孙瓒，兴兵前来，何劳元帅亲自出马？末将不才，愿讨一支将令，大战\n公孙瓒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看你小小年纪，面黄肌瘦，岂是他人对手？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅你好小量人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "元帅把人太小量，\n细听赵云说端详：\n海水焉能用斗量！"
        },
        {
          "character": "英雄岂在容貌上、袁绍",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赵云说话太张狂，\n不由老夫怒胸膛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "英雄岂在容貌上、袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大赵云，本帅正要出兵，你在帐中，絮絮叨叨。\n来，叉出帐去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起兵前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四下手、二将、公孙瓒同上，对阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙瓒",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见袁绍，气满胸，\n大骂无志狗奸雄：\n乱箭穿身为哪宗？\n割去尔的牛头，方解俺气满胸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我命二弟把信送、老爷兴兵威风勇、袁绍",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "公孙说话理不通，\n西凉马腾把路横。\n埋怨老夫为哪宗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "你弟被他把命送、公孙瓒",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "诡计多端害人命，\n擅敢狂言来逞能！\n少时叫尔丧残生！\n（公孙瓒、袁绍同起打，公孙瓒败下，袁绍、四龙套、四上手、颜良、文丑、吕翔同追下。颜良上，二将同"
        }
