      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公孙瓒上，袁绍、四龙套同追上，公孙瓒落马。赵云上，起打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "袁绍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵云，你反了么！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得多言，看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（袁绍、四龙套同败下，赵云追下，公孙瓒看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙瓒",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "颜良、文丑武艺精，\n将吾挑下马能行。\n忽然来了一英雄。\n舍身救我为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云上，四龙套同上，对阵，四龙套同败下。赵云转身，公孙瓒泣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙瓒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请转。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙瓒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问将军，尊姓大名，为何奋勇救我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，姓赵名云，字子龙，乃常山人氏，在袁绍帐下为将。可恨老贼，目不识人，\n藐视英雄，叫我在磐河牧马。适才闻得喊杀之声，是俺登高望见，将军大败，\n故而前来相救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙瓒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军如此侠义，愿与将军结为金兰，请到营中一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。公孙瓒、赵云同下。）"
        }
      ],
